直踩<br />\n最低限度我講緊連登呢度 唔好一盤散沙<br />\n利申港獨派"},{"pid":"3cb0d1f3a253118d93cc843ae0cea4455fd3784d","tid":728394,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"本土派做嘅嘢例如貼大字報其實係有用<br />\n蘇共以前宣傳亦都係靠貼大字報<br />\n只不過本土派入面嘅內容過於偏激<br />\n一嚟就同香港人宣揚最高級別嘅思想<br />\n大部份都係話咩奪回香港乜乜物物<br />\n每次都咁 關注自己利益嘅香港人點會比自己以身犯險"},{"pid":"a38f743d50ae1be926ccc21e98d1a6a9663bad74","tid":728394,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"915063420d29d3f13b34523c52b1df64ff2e79e4","tid":728394,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T03:55:37.000Z","msg":"我想問下樓主<br />\n你覺唔覺得范國威, 劉慧卿，梁耀忠, 楊岳橋係有心反共先?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好借啲意抹黑本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T08:06:25.000Z","msg":"況且有啲人唔係本土 但亦非泛民<br />\n亦都會被攻擊 呢個問題令反共排一直一盤散沙<br />\n並唔係針對你哋本土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係知出一個依家存在嘅問題"},{"pid":"c707ce1b4c2cac2b6e13bee908a3bf75e7a93b4c","tid":728394,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0048f4bd6a728778d69d2c559bae8e48844e7d30","tid":728394,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T03:51:42.000Z","msg":"亂咁捉毛?<br />\n邊隻捉錯咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好quote完高學歷廢青個post<br />\n然後自說自話偷換概念喎柒頭<br />\n呢啲招數一睇就睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T08:07:41.000Z","msg":"蔣仔算唔算係一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}